                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18450512-1221-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18450512-1221-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18450512-1221-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 1 purse, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 3 sovereigns, and 5 shillings; the monies of <persName id="t18450512-name-1088" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450512-name-1088" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450512-name-1088" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
